Package: mvaplots
Title: Multiverse Analysis Visualization Plots
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Yuanyuan", "Qu", email = "Yuanyuan.Qu@campus.lmu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to visualize multiverse analysis results. 
    Includes a density plot comparing all vs. significant outcomes, heatmap strips 
    showing analytical decisions, and a top-level function to combine both into 
    one multiverse plot.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
